{"tid":1769431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【核彈？】東方：在黑社會人士搜出伸縮警棍","createTime":"2019-12-05T01:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T01:46:31.000Z","uid":320881,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7d108938b4dec94a8279b268d1047bac48732b","tid":1769431,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:25:42.000Z","msg":"警員調查下發現該輛七人車掛上假牌，在本年11月於元朗區報失，匙膽位置被掏空，證實是一輛失車，並<span style=\"color: red;\">在司機位地氈底搜出一支伸縮警棍</span>。被捕女司機身上沒有發現違禁品，警犬到場搜車並無發現。經調查後，被捕女司機涉嫌瘋狂駕駛、停牌駕駛、偷車、無第三者保險、使用虛假文書、藏有違禁武器等最少6宗罪被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，被捕29歲女司機有黑社會背景</span>，居於屯門寶田邨，有販毒案底，為區內大拆家，經常給邨內拆家散貨。<br />\n<br />\nSource:  <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191205/mobile/bkn-20191205025432372-1205_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191205%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191205025432372-1205_00822_001.html&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=738586a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191205/mobile/bkn-20191205025432372-1205_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n黑社會有伸縮警棍<br />\n係鄧小強獲派發？<br />\n定係<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警遺失武器唔駛同公眾交代</span>？<br />\n如果係後者，今日就只係黑警開槍殺人，遲下黑社會開槍殺人都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"38e6e06fcb3c31f2ddcf313864f67b4d59f70af6","tid":1769431,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁，求推上去比大家睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cee79526dd23676da311609a7c9031931903bf6","tid":1769431,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"其實唔難買。。。"},{"pid":"9096c7fd0a406bd149f2c9054e7eb676620bf6b8","tid":1769431,"uid":43178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"黑社會有伸縮警棍有咩問題<br />\n佢哋咪黑社會囉"},{"pid":"1259b09da4c78513eca80c45b9abc234f76971b2","tid":1769431,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite